00:16:19.880 --> 00:16:21.140
para segurar Jiang Lin.

00:16:22.840 --> 00:16:23.440
Ah, pois.

00:16:24.440 --> 00:16:25.160
Quando vai a tribunal

00:16:25.160 --> 00:16:26.720
