[Assassino de marido]

00:22:21.170 --> 00:22:22.660
[Assassino de marido]

00:22:26.420 --> 00:22:27.460
[Assassino de marido]

00:22:38.000 --> 00:22:38.800
Lu Si Yu!

00:22:40.360 --> 00:22:41.120
Sim, Haimeng?

00:23:00.240 --> 00:23:01.640
O que quer exatamente?

